This is according to a new report issued at the 'Roll Back Malaria Partnership to End Malaria' conference in Abuja, Nigeria. The survey is the first systematic attempt in many years to collate expert African views on malaria policy. For more on this, Samora Mangesi spoke to Bob Snow, Professor of Malaria Epidemiology at the University of Oxford, and Co-chair of the new study... --ChannelAfrica--